title: ASTRO wrap up their season series with 'Winter Dream'! | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me ASTRO wrap up their season series with 'Winter Dream'! By jennywill 21 minutes ago 1,985 265 4 1 Google+ ASTRO has released the final piece to their seasonal series!
The boys debuted with ' Spring Up ' last year, came back in the summer with ' Summer Vibes ', and then again in the fall with ' Autumn Story '. They're now bringing the series to a close with ' Winter Dream ' and title song " Should've Held On ". The single includes two other songs - " Cotton Candy " and " You & Me (Thanks AROHA) ". The last song is a fan song with lyrics by the entire group. 
ASTRO will also be celebrating their 1st anniversary since debut this February 23.
